{"tid":2283989,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【投票機制】樂迷結果佔七成","createTime":"2020-11-13T03:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T14:53:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea1567e1e698f93d7f9238801e207aec441468c","tid":2283989,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:31:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201113/6ZXMOFI6FNEHDNCSNX3EYJCKDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201113%2F6ZXMOFI6FNEHDNCSNX3EYJCKDU%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BykV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=5f9c751b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201113%2F6ZXMOFI6FNEHDNCSNX3EYJCKDU%2F&h=1ef4e3ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201113/6ZXMOFI6FNEHDNCSNX3EYJCKDU/</a><br />\n<br />\n【投票機制】樂迷結果佔七成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uBdag17glagw7T_iMEf1Vi1aT74=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AG5QJKQ6GZHSDGPULVAS6AWQG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuBdag17glagw7T_iMEf1Vi1aT74%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAG5QJKQ6GZHSDGPULVAS6AWQG4.jpg&h=b64151bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港台《第43屆十大中文金曲頒獎典禮》將於明年1月16日錄播，網上投票已在進行中。在港台頒獎禮一眾獎項中，金曲獎、國語歌曲獎、新人獎、男歌手獎、女歌手獎、樂隊/組合獎及至尊金曲獎等，評分準則是樂迷投票佔70%；而專業評選團則佔30%，因此投票對結果是十分之重要。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港台頒獎禮網上投票 手足齊撐同路歌手  方皓玟《人話》爭至尊金曲 延續黃色音樂圈<br />\n<br />\n至於入圍準則，只要歌曲、歌手、樂隊或組合曾登上中文歌曲龍虎榜三甲位置，皆自動成為候選歌曲及男、女歌手獎等人選。國語歌曲獎則只要曾上中文歌曲龍虎榜便可加入候選。"},{"pid":"c365438480ec36d3bd78c5b2e1496adb12728a45","tid":2283989,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:39:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">11月15日截止！</span></strong></span><b